<HL>
   Politics &amp; Policy:
   Senate Fails to Override
   Veto on Easing Hatch Act
</HL>
<DATE>
06/22/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
</SO>
<CO>
   LABOR
</CO>
